places.address: Bara Dare Wali Masjid, Saray Tulsiram, Jansath, Uttar Pradesh 251314

featured_reviews.review_id: Bara Dare Wali Masjid located in Sarai TulsiRam Jansath. It's really a good place to pray. In this area lower middle class family live in majority. Along with the masjid a Madrasa is also there. It's known as Madrasa  Kanjul Uloom. If I say honestly the management of the mosque is in weak hands. Area around the masjid is financially weak so they are not in the condition to contribute for Mosque. This mosque is located at the end point. Sarai Tulsi Ram is a colony where every community live happily. The major profession of the people of colony is labouring and Farming.
